    description: "By joining the Bitcoin District Initiative, you're contributing to a future where DC residents and local businesses can achieve true financial independence and digital autonomy through Bitcoin education. Your efforts help us meet people where they are, navigate a complex landscape, champion privacy and self-custody, and foster a collaborative community rooted in trust and principled innovation. Together, we're building a grassroots movement that empowers everyone to explore Bitcoin's potential for hope, resilience, and self-sovereigntyâ€”regardless of background.",
